g.text: In this exercise you combine data by concatenating and joining tables.
Join the information on the online purchases with the prices of the products
Join the "TransactionsOnline" and "ProductNrAndPrize" tables directly on the database (DB Joiner)
Read the joined table into KNIME
Add the location information to each purchase in a store based on the StoreID (Joiner node)
Concatenate customer information data from the two different systems into one table
Convert the "Newsletter" column from number to string in the table from the system 1
Concatenate the customer data from the two systems
